The purpose of this study is to provide safety and efficacy data for the X-Suit NIR(R) Covered Biliary Metallic Stent for subjects with malignant stricture(s) in the biliary tree.

 The study is designed to support the regulatory requirement of a 510(k) marketing application in the United States.

